g.text: The Inexor Tree is the unit of two contemplary APIs on C++ (Inexor Core) and NodeJS-side (Inexor Flex) to access a shared set of variables.
Additionally the Inexor Tree can be synchronized in the future with distributed PCs, of which some can interact as master, some as slave.
On all sites reactions on state changes of the tree can be attached to the variables.
But some are reserved for higher priority members of the playerbase (admins, moderators, server owners, local players).
Each Variable of the Tree is automatically synced with remote Inexor Core and Inexor Flex versions as well by default. Yet they can always opt-out.
